{"tid":2225051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬鞍山六旬翁拒戴口罩行超市 發難襲警被捕","createTime":"2020-10-01T04:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T04:59:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2fcc4fe15e786ec3eafd7e8b25723001f40ae9","tid":2225051,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"警方昨日於馬鞍山以涉嫌襲警拘捕一名60歲男子，有一名警員頭部受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日下午2時許接獲馬鞍山恒安邨一間超市職員報案，指一名中年男子在超市因拒絕戴口罩而與超市職員爭執。警員接報到場後勸諭涉事的葉姓男子戴口罩，惟葉男情緒激動，不聽勸諭，更揮拳襲擊一名男警員的頭部。警員隨即制服葉男，並以涉嫌襲警將其拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n被襲擊的男警員清醒，其後被送往威爾斯親王醫院治理，案件交由沙田警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 頭條"},{"pid":"5fbaac03de3903c947c081bf1fab4c9577e013be","tid":2225051,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:34:32.000Z","msg":"惠康？"},{"pid":"00634cd74e4c4d196608578c9c9111b4a0f088b6","tid":2225051,"uid":43062,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291fd478c033129eefb2350be77a7e98191d0daf","tid":2225051,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:35:56.000Z","msg":"唔知依件襲警又判幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569e53055e9a952c905d4f1ba9881620766b32fe","tid":2225051,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef20cbc12e296a4b21710136830396648c941ae","tid":2225051,"uid":23433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:37:36.000Z","msg":"屠龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277340947303ff32e3c0822ab7339a21e18fb18e","tid":2225051,"uid":243855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"頭部受傷=爆暗瘡？"},{"pid":"40b5d59efac36